      <bioghist id="aspace_41004e6cba6c252d36867bfe6d798879">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Organized by the African American house (now Afro-American Cultural Center) in the 1970s, the Black Tie Society was a program that promoted interaction between African American Studies faculty and students at Yale.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_8fb02548d1fc4ea70f61e01525efb4d0">
